# Privacy Policy Outline – AgriTech Platform (GRC Case Study)

## 1. Introduction & Scope

This document outlines the data protection approach for a digital AgriTech platform designed to connect farmers with experts, provide AI-based crop risk analysis, and facilitate access to agricultural resources and services.

The platform processes personal data from users located in Colombia and, where applicable, the European Union.

---

## 2. Applicable Legal Framework

This policy is aligned with the following regulations:

### Colombia
- Law 1581 of 2012 (Personal Data Protection Law)
- Decree 1377 of 2013
- Guidelines issued by the Superintendence of Industry and Commerce (SIC)

### European Union
- General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)

The platform adopts principles such as lawfulness, transparency, purpose limitation, data minimization, and accountability.

---

